<div class="jumbotron" id="welcome">
  <div class="container">
    <a name="welcome"><h1>Welcome</h1></a>
    <h1>Mario's Speciality Food Products</h1>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="jumbotron" id="about">
  <div class="container">
    <a name="about"><h1>About Marios</h1></a>
    <p><em>Marios</em> was founded in 1983 on Hawthorne Boulevard in Southeast Portland, and over the years has built a reputation as one of the great European-style markets in the United States.</p>
    <p><em>Marios</em> is famous for itâ€™s housemade fresh pastas (extruded, sheet and ravioli) using the highest quality Northwest-grown wheat and eggs. Additionally, our in-house kitchen prepares fresh pasta sauces, and an array of delicious prepared foods.</p>
    <p>But <em>Marios</em> isn't just about pasta. There is also a revered selection of Mediterranean wines (with a strong focus on Italian), cheese cases unparalleled in the Northwest, and extraordinary food products sourced locally, regionally, nationally and internationally.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="jumbotron" id="scopes">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-sm-6" id="popular">
      <a name="popular"><h2>Check out the Most Talked about Product:</h2></a>
        <ul>
          <% @products.mostReviews.each do |product| %>
            <li><%= link_to product.name, product_path(product) %></li>
          <% end %>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-6" id="new">
        <a name="new"><h2>These products have recently been added:</h2></a>
        <ul>
          <% @products.mostRecent.each do |product| %>
            <li><%= link_to product.name, product_path(product) %></li>
          <% end %>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="jumbotron" id="products">
  <div class="container">
    <a name="products"><h1>Products</h1></a>
    <%= image_tag "wine.jpg", {id: 'wine'} %>
    <ul>
      <% @products.each do |product| %>
        <li><%= link_to product.name, product_path(product) %></li>
      <% end %>
    </ul>
    <br>
    <%= link_to "Add a New Product", new_product_path, {class: 'btn btn-default'}%>

  </div>
</div>
